text.tspan: Hey mom. I ... no, I don't
know if you can do that.
Yes, I'm a law student, but no,
I can't give you legal advice.
Have you tried ... look, it's really
hard doing this over the phone.
No, not even a small one!
Have you -- Dad, hey, I don't care
what the neighbors said. I'm not
dropping a bomb on their house.
Yeah, I know I said that, but
Cite as: Andrew Fong, Help, TORT BUNNIES (October 11, 2010), http://tortbunnies.com/56.html.
